OL,3,CRecords may not exist for car finance
OL,4,Ccompensation, says car loan industry
OL,6,FDrivers might not have the records
OL,7,Fneeded to get motor finance
OL,8,Fcompensation, the car loan industry
OL,9,Fhas warned.
OL,11,FMillions of car owners could receive a
OL,12,Fpayout after the Financial Conduct
OL,13,FAuthority (FCA) announced it would set
OL,14,Fup a compensation scheme for people
OL,15,Fwho were unlawfully sold car finance,
OL,16,Funaware their car dealership was
OL,17,Freceiving a commission from the
OL,18,Ffinance company.
