OL,3,CRecords may not exist for car finance
OL,4,Ccompensation, says car loan industry
OL,6,FThe regulator said many motor finance
OL,7,Ffirms had not complied with the law
OL,8,Fdating back to 2007 and it would
OL,9,Fdecide how affected customers should
OL,10,Fbe compensated.
OL,12,FFCA chief executive Nikhil Rathi said
OL,13,Fthe consultation process would work
OL,14,Fout the rules of the scheme, establish
OL,15,Fwho should be included and how
OL,16,Fcompensation should be paid.
