OL,6,F"The loan companies will have to
OL,7,Ffollow those rules to make sure they
OL,8,Fcomply and if they don't, there'll be
OL,9,Flegal consequences for them," he told
OL,10,FITV News.
OL,12,F"If the law has been broken, everybody
OL,13,Fshould be making best efforts to put
OL,14,Fit right."
OL,16,FBut the director general of the
OL,17,FFinance and Leasing Association
OL,18,FStephen Haddrill said the FCA needed
OL,19,Fto address the issue of missing
OL,20,Fpaperwork, as many of the claims were
OL,21,Fup to 18 years old.
