OL,6,F"We have concerns about whether it is
OL,7,Fpossible to have a fair redress scheme
OL,8,Fthat goes back to 2007 when firms have
OL,9,Fnot been required to hold such dated
OL,10,Finformation and the evidence base will
OL,11,Fbe patchy at best," he said.
OL,13,FMr Rathi said the FCA would work
OL,14,Fthrough those issues.
OL,16,F"We're going to work with firms now to
OL,17,Fwork out what is operationally
OL,18,Fpossible," he explained.
