OL,6,FHe said the suggested amount was too
OL,7,Flow and should be up to #3500.
OL,9,F"It will be nice to know that others
OL,10,Fwill get something back after the mess
OL,11,Fthey made," he told ITV News.
OL,13,F"It should be a lot more than
OL,14,Fhundreds, a couple thousand max,
OL,15,Fconsidering what we've had to go
OL,16,Fthrough."
OL,18,FThe consultation will begin by early
OL,19,FOctober and if the compensation scheme
OL,20,Fgoes ahead, the first payments should
OL,21,Fbe made in 2026.
